    "Previously, Zhang et al.",
    "introduced an innovative approach known as hybrid-tuning, aimed at addressing the challenge of catastrophic forgetting (Zhang et al. 2023a).",
    "This method seamlessly merges both general and domain-specific knowledge, while also harmonizing the stages of pre-training and fine-tuning.",
    "The result is a system that excels in delivering precise and contextually fitting responses within the specific Chinese domain.",
    "It is worth noting that such a method holds significant promise for extending its applicability to emerging emotional tasks."
